{
  "stem": "23599.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and that is what happened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the-- so-- I stayed together-- [INAUDIBLE] our husbands were first cousins.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But her husband was taken when they were taking the-- the-- people-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the best known people, the 10 people, they were us.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that was one of them, was the husband.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was very active in-- in-- in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he was taken.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But she, somehow, she found herself another friend.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was amazing how that went, you know, people who lost their husbands and their-- their mothers or fathers and how they-- how they somehow-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] somehow got it over and found someone else.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so she found a very-- a very close friend she had.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he was working in-- in the office where they make the lists-- where he made the lists.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We went in-- in that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I didn't ask him to put me on the list.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I knew if he can, he will.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I won't have to ask him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was the evening before we went to Auschwitz, before the transport went.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He came to my cousin, you know, and said to her that he was able to put me on the list.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think I told you that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was able to-- there was one opening.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he put me on the list.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But he said, remember, tell her that she will have to go to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And who-- we knew who goes to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But you never know who comes out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And the-- and the horn was blowing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And everybody had to get out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But there was a woman that Schindler had [INAUDIBLE], sent.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Schindler had sent, because we were there already three weeks.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
